    <h2>Use Cases</h2>
    <!-- Unordered list (>= 1) with descriptive bullets -->
    <ul>
      <li><span class="accent-blue"><b>Post-discharge monitoring:</b></span> Home devices reduce readmissions with trend alerts and shared reports.</li>
      <li><span class="accent-green"><b>Chronic care support:</b></span> Wearables nudge adherence and visualize improvements over weeks, not days.</li>
      <li><b>Clinic throughput:</b> Standardized supplies make room turnover faster and reduce pick-list errors.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How to Choose the Right Product</h3>
    <!-- Ordered list (>= 1) with clear steps -->
    <ol>
      <li><b>Define your goal:</b> Monitoring vs. recovery vs. prevention.</li>
      <li><b>Check compatibility:</b> Mobile OS, EMR exports, and data-sharing needs.</li>
      <li><b>Plan lifecycle:</b> Warranty coverage, replacements, and training needs.</li>
    </ol>

